# CloudFlare Architecture Diagram Tool

This project is an interactive system architecture diagram tool built with React and hosted on Cloudflare Pages.

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend**: React + Vite
- **Diagram Library**: React Flow
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS
- **Hosting**: Cloudflare Pages

## Project Structure
- `/src` - React application source code
- `/src/components` - React components (DiagramCanvas, ToggleSidebar, etc.)
- `/src/data` - Component definitions and initial diagram data
- `/public` - Static assets

## Key Features
- Toggle visibility of architecture components
- Drag and drop diagram elements
- Hover tooltips with component details
- Session-based state (no persistence)

## Development
```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

## Deployment
```bash
npm run build
npx wrangler pages deploy dist
```
